data.value:
appear as offline 1. Click “go offline”. 2. Login in to your League of Legends Client. to go online again just click "go online" - you don't have to log in again
don't receive messages (recommended for streaming) 1. Login in to your League of Legends Client. 2. Click “go offline”. Your LoL-friends can see that you are online, but you don't receive messages You won’t be able to see messages in champ select neither can you write but Ingame all is the same as it used to be. (All- and Teamchat) 3. If your chat section isn’t disabled click a random chat, so it will refresh the connection. 4. Click “go online” to receive messages. 5. If your chat section isn’t enabled, click a random chat, so it will refresh the connection.
